{"tid":770373,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【股神炒啲乜】巴郡增持蘋果至5.1% 持股市值達515億美元","createTime":"2018-08-07T04:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T04:51:34.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"89deacba9727585c519a7f39cc8d5ee40ab48680","tid":770373,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T04:50:17.000Z","msg":"「股神」畢菲特旗下投資旗艦巴郡，日前公布業績後，繼續增持蘋果公司股份。根據最新監管文件披露，巴郡上季增持267萬股蘋果股份，截至6月底，巴郡持有的蘋果股份約2.465億股，持股量5.1%，以昨日蘋果收市價209.06美元計，巴郡持有的蘋果股份市值高達515.3億美元。<br />\n<br />\n畢菲特早前表示，自己非常喜歡蘋果及高層的管理方式及作風，自己及巴郡會盡可能買入蘋果的股份。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180807/large/1533606882_8b91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180807%2Flarge%2F1533606882_8b91.jpg&h=98b120c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴郡增持蘋果至5.1% 持股市值達515億美元<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180807/58532588\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180807%2F58532588&d=HyTeR31y2n6e9uAjay0mD7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=4cd9a627\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180807%2F58532588&h=5cccdb4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180807/58532588</a>"},{"pid":"01f502803dd49828d974b929321c58731df08ef4","tid":770373,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T04:51:34.000Z","msg":"廢老 識炒一定炒屌米"}]}